<div class="story-text">
<% if !@pocket.include?("Keys")%>
  <p>
  As you leave your house, you suddenly remember: MY KEYS!
  </p>

  <p>
  Check your pockets to make sure they're there... otherwise this is going to be a whole different kind of game.
  </p>
<% else %>
  <p>
  You stand idly outside your door, with a gnawing feeling that you usually do something when you step outside the house.
  </p>
<% end%>
<% flash.each do |type, msg| %>
  <div class ="alert">
    <%= msg %>
  </div>
<% end %>

<% if @door_locked %>
  <p>
    The cool air hits you and you can and the scent of your hometown ‘SOMETHING’ fills your nostrils. 
    As you recently volunteered for a medical research trial, 
    your memory is a little hazy and can't exactly remember how to get to Big Boys Burger. You’re presented with two options: left or right.
  </p>

  <span>
    <%= link_to "Left", '/game/page3', class: "page5-button" %>
    <%= link_to "Right", '/game/page4', class: "page5-button" %>
  </span>
<% else %>
  <%= link_to "Lock Door", '/game/lock-door', class: "page5-button"%>
<% end %>
<%= link_to "Go back", '/game/page1', class: "page5-button" %>

</div>
